Package: didhelpers
Title: Diagnostic and Visualization Utilities for Difference-in-Differences Designs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Stefano", "Graziosi", , "stefano.graziosi@studbocconi.it", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Lightweight diagnostic and visualization utilities for staggered
    difference-in-differences designs. Provides functions for plotting treatment
    timing, testing pre-trends via event-study regressions, summarizing
    Goodman-Bacon (2021) decomposition weights, and generating comprehensive
    diagnostic reports.
